Card:
	Knows:
		-Suit it is
		-Face value
		-Color
		-Face-up or face-down
	It can:
		-Flip over

Deck:
	Knows:
		-Cards in it and order of cards
		-Number of top card
	It can:
		-Draw
		-Shuffle
		-Be searched
		
Spells:
	Knows:
		-Cards needed to activate it
		-Order in which cards need to be done
		-Name of spell
		-Description of spell